# Workspace-root .npmrc — scope mapping for the @n3ary GitHub Packages
# registry. Auth token is NOT here (pnpm 11 refuses to expand env vars
# in project .npmrc, and committing one would leak it to anyone with
# read access). CI passes `NODE_AUTH_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.NPM_TOKEN }}`
# (a fine-grained PAT with packages:read for @n3ary/gtfs-spec); pnpm 11
# auto-discovers that env var for *.pkg.github.com scopes.
#
# After switching to NPM_TOKEN, the pr-validation.yml in this repo
# also supplies it the same way.
@n3ary:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
